AS HORDES OF
SUMMER-STARVED TEENAGERS

03:21.469 --> 03:24.438
DESCEND ON UNSUSPECTING
FLAGSTAFF, ARIZONA,

03:24.505 --> 03:26.740
LET'S SEE WHAT THESE TWO
POISED YOUNG WOMEN

03:26.807 --> 03:28.876
