THE LAST DAY OF SCHOOL!

03:28.942 --> 03:32.713
- I'M OUTTA HERE, RIVERDALE!
- YEAH, SCHOOL'S OUT, BABY!

03:32.780 --> 03:35.783
ALL RIGHT.
THE CAMERA LOVES YOU.

03:35.849 --> 03:38.118
SO, LAUREN, WHAT ARE
YOU DOING TONIGHT?

03:38.185 --> 03:39.587
