ON MY FRIEND.

03:39.653 --> 03:41.522
WHATEVER YOU'RE
DOING TONIGHT.

03:41.589 --> 03:43.557
LAUREN, STOP HITTING
ON MY BROTHER. UGH!

03:43.624 --> 03:45.293
HEY, WOULD YOU TELL MOM
I'LL BE LATE?

03:45.359 --> 03:47.227
BUT IT'S YOUR GRADUATION
BARBECUE.

03:47.295 --> 03:50.798
I'VE GOT PLACES
TO GO, PEOPLE TO SEE.
JUST SAVE ME A BURNT BURGER.

03:50.864 --> 03:52.766
- WILL YOU GIVE ME
A RIDE HOME?
- SURE.

